# New Hire Onboarding Checklist (Template)

A reusable checklist for onboarding a new employee, covering pre-start through end of first month.

## Before Day 1
- [ ] Offer letter and contract signed
- [ ] IT equipment and system access requested
- [ ] Workspace / remote setup confirmed
- [ ] Welcome email sent with first-day details

## Day 1
- [ ] Welcome and team introductions
- [ ] Workstation and login access confirmed working
- [ ] Company policies and handbook shared
- [ ] Health & safety / compliance briefing

## Week 1
- [ ] Role expectations and KPIs discussed with manager
- [ ] Key stakeholders and cross-team contacts introduced
- [ ] Initial training scheduled
- [ ] Check-in with HR

## First Month
- [ ] 30-day check-in with manager
- [ ] Feedback collected on onboarding experience
- [ ] Any outstanding access/equipment issues resolved
- [ ] Goals set for next 60 days

---
*Adapt this checklist per department or role as needed.*
